name: Cinderfish Development
body:
# Cinderfish Development
A group of lazy devs who write tools and apps so we don't have to do things manually.

## What's a Cinderfish?
It's a fish tied to a cinderblock.

## What? Why?
A few things:
- It describes an app that runs/swims like a fish tied to a cinderblock
- It's a comment in a conversation that is so out of place that it sinks the rest of the conversation.
